EkVulkan - 
    Handles Instance extensions, layers, and Creation.
    Also Picks PhysDev, and Handles Device Extensions and Layers as well as creation
    Handles Destruction of components.

    Contains Window.
    Creates CommandPool Interfaces.

    Manages Queues and Queue Families.

    also handles creation of Window.

EkCmdPool -
    Wraps commandpool and EkCmdBuffer Creation

EkCmdBuffer -
    Wraps Vulkan Commands in an easy to use c++ class

